    "display_name": "Ethel Ryker",
    "avatar": "characters/Ethel_veX.jpg",
    "content": "My grandfather. Maybe not in biology. But in mind, in every way that matters, in every room he walked into. You were our rock. Not spiritual. Just real. Just there. Always there.",
